CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 9, 1946, pg. 32, reads: "Feted on Natal Day - Mrs. Frances Harris, active member of Ebenezer Baptist Church, was honored by her children on her birthday last Saturday evening. The party was held at the home of a son, Cornelius Harris, of Milwaukee Street. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Women, men, and children gathered for birthday of Frances Harris in home of Cornelius Harris with photographs on wall and mantle in background, Milwaukee Street, Upper Hill District
